com.cgoab.offline.client
Interface UploadClient

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractUploadClient, DefaultWebUploadClient, MockClient
public interface UploadClient

An API that encapsulates the "operations" needed to uploaded pages and photos to the CGOAB server.

Operations execute asynchronously however only one operation can ever be in progress at a given time. An IllegalStateException is thrown if this constraint is violated. Typically the callback passed into an operation will be used to listen for completion before proceeding with the next operation and so on.
